      "description": "## 🧾 **Cliplet v0.3.1**\r\n\r\n### **Overview**\r\n\r\nThis release adds the ability to copy cliplet content directly to the system clipboard and updates the icons used for creating and editing cliplets.\r\n  \r\n### **Changes**\r\n\r\n✨ **Copy cliplet to system clipboard**\r\nA new action allows users to copy a cliplet’s content directly to the OS clipboard without inserting it into the editor.\r\n  \r\n<img width=\"778\" height=\"450\" alt=\"copy-to-clipboard\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3b198c8a-540e-49f4-b437-02079abe1373\" />\r\n\r\n🎨 **Updated creation and editing icons**\r\nThe icons for creating and editing cliplets have been updated.\r\n  \r\n\r\n🔧 **Minor improvements and fixes**\r\nIncludes small internal adjustments and miscellaneous fixes.",
