      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## **🧾 Cliplet v0.3.0**\r\n\r\n### **Overview**\r\n\r\nA feature-focused update that makes Cliplet more flexible and powerful.\r\nThis release introduces **placeholders**, allowing you to create dynamic cliplet templates.\r\n\r\n### **Changes**\r\n\r\n✨ **New placeholders:**\r\n\r\nYou can now use special markers inside cliplet content:\r\n- {cursor} — moves the cursor to that position after insertion\r\n- {clipboard} — inserts your current OS clipboard text\r\n\r\n<img width=\"537\" height=\"444\" alt=\"edit\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2c6b9bdf-d742-4f4a-84d4-18a13636ae34\" />\r\n<img width=\"536\" height=\"446\" alt=\"view\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f9ca2910-8cc2-4847-9d16-fb232026faec\" />\r\n",
