      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## 🧾 Cliplet v0.2.1\r\n\r\n### Overview\r\nA small update focused on polish and consistency.  \r\nThis release improves the command behavior and overall stability — no action required from users.\r\n\r\n### Changes\r\n- ✨ **Improved usability:**  \r\n  The `Add Cliplet` command is now available only when text is selected, preventing accidental execution.\r\n- 💬 **Unified messages:**  \r\n  The “not found” notice shown in certain cases is now clearer and consistent.\r\n- 🧩 **Internal improvements:**  \r\n  Refactored code and styling for better maintainability and consistency.\r\n\r\n### Compatibility\r\nNo breaking changes. All your data and settings remain safe.",
